headline: Are Cboe’s New Tech Partnerships a Catalyst for Its Strong 2025 Price Rally?
summary: Curious if Cboe Global Markets might be undervalued right now? You are not alone, especially with the market looking for the next big opportunity in financial infrastructure stocks. The stock has posted eye-catching returns, rising 3.9% over the last week, 7.3% this past month, a strong 33.0% year-to-date, and an impressive 34.3% over the last twelve months.
